{"tid":50804,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"★仲有冇Lihkg仔記得呢個節目-----TVB每日一字？","createTime":"2016-12-22T17:13:21.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-23T10:10:45.000Z","uid":19454,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"6c530dadb2deb4b7ee65632327cfd55eb5f806ce","tid":50804,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-22T17:13:21.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://zh.wikipedia.org/wiki/每日一字_(香港)\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fzh.wikipedia.org%2Fwiki%2F%E6%AF%8F%E6%97%A5%E4%B8%80%E5%AD%97_%28%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF%29&d=puiSddp9Vo3i8vVDNE0kXQT5PszEexF2%2B6H4LydsHP4%3D&h=18822bc0\" target=\"_blank\">https://zh.wikipedia.org/wiki/每日一字_(香港)</a><br />\n<br />\n香港的《每日一字》，是香港無線電視於1983年至1987年所播放的一個資訊節目，由林佐瀚主持，於每天18:25播放（每集約3分鐘）。每天都會介紹1個中文字。介紹其正確讀音、用法，及糾正人們對該字的誤解，深受歡迎。在三年多的時間，林佐瀚教曉觀眾過千字。"},{"pid":"16265d2132756efcc61c4839bc4c89ed35967180","tid":50804,"uid":21181,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-22T17:13:46.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"84d3754351c13d2c186bd465084b67884139f720","tid":50804,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-22T17:14:16.000Z","msg":"見Lihkg仔咁有興趣中文字，特意推介"},{"pid":"662787c7a2e6aaf292c1718ea032e15eca86ce3f","tid":50804,"uid":49392,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-22T17:16:06.000Z","msg":"未出世<br />\n認字特警<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/42.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1dd553471e57c4dbb480b8de7ee4309868b064a6","tid":50804,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-22T17:16:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://www.jidianzaixian.com/Uploads/userUploads/DeadPhotos/e63f5c0c-6cd9-45c9-8666-6ea029f5e33d.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.jidianzaixian.com%2FUploads%2FuserUploads%2FDeadPhotos%2Fe63f5c0c-6cd9-45c9-8666-6ea029f5e33d.jpg&h=644a8621&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">Lihkg仔，你好！</span>"},{"pid":"462ec